    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six and a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. This example benefits from documented VANOS servicing and proactive rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring the structural integrity of the monocoque remains uncompromised. The drivetrain exhibits linear power delivery up to the 8,000 RPM redline, with the mechanical limited-slip differential providing excellent torque vectoring. While showing minor signs of use consistent with its age, the suspension remains taut with refreshed bushings, and the throttle response is razor-sharp thanks to the factory individual throttle bodies. A driver\u2019s spec car with the critical preventative maintenance already completed.",
