    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This 2018 Luxury AWD SUV is the perfect blend of performance and practicality. Finished in a stunning Midnight Blue Metallic, the exterior remains vibrant, showing only the expected minor road wear and small stone chips consistent with careful use. Inside, you\u2019ll find a smoke-free cabin appointed with supple Sahara Tan leather; while there is light natural creasing on the driver's seat bolster, the interior remains remarkably clean and free of stains or tears. Every feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the premium surround-sound system and navigation, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle has been meticulously cared for, with a complete service history and a recent multi-point inspection confirming the engine and transmission are in robust health. It rides on a set of high-quality all-season tires with significant tread remaining. This is a reliable, turn-key vehicle that offers a premium driving experience for the discerning buyer who appreciates a well-documented history.",
      "price": 36500.0,
